                                <span class="sign"></span> How long are listings active?
                            </a>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-heading -->

                        <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-body collapse" style="height: 0px; ">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                Listings are active for @AnarkRE.Globals.ListingDays days by default.
                            </div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
                    </div><!-- /.accordion-group -->

                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq1" href="#collapse2">
                                <span class="sign"></span> How are listings priced?
                            </a>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-heading -->

                        <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                The price of a listing can be pegged to the currency of your choice. Prices are determined using the Bitpay data feed.</div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
                    </div><!-- /.accordion-group -->

                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq1" href="#collapseC">
                                <span class="sign"></span> What are product variations?
                            </a>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-heading -->

                        <div id="collapseC" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                If you would like your buyer to specify some selection such as color or size, you can add a product variation.<br /><br />
                                This option can be found on a listing page you created under the "Add More" tab.
                            </div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
                    </div><!-- /.accordion-group -->

                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq1" href="#collapseD">
                                <span class="sign"></span> Can I offer different shipping options?
                            </a>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-heading -->

                        <div id="collapseD" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                Yes. After creating a listing, select the "Add More" tab and you can add up to @AnarkRE.Globals.ListAddOpts[AnarkRE.ListingAdditionType.Shipping] different shipping options.
                                <br /><br />
                                The customer must select one of the shipping methods you input and the cost will be added to the total.
                            </div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
