                            </div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
                    </div><!-- /.accordion-group -->

                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq3" href="#collapse10">
                                <span class="sign"></span> How can I reset my account password?
                            </a>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-heading -->

                        <div id="collapse10" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                Password reset coming soon, till then <a href="mailto:support@anark.it">email us</a></div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
                    </div><!-- /.accordion-group -->

                    <div class="accordion-group">
                        <div class="accordion-heading">
                            <a class="accordion-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#faq3" href="#collapseB">
                                <span class="sign"></span> How does feedback work?
                            </a>
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-heading -->

                        <div id="collapseB" class="accordion-body collapse">
                            <div class="accordion-inner">
                                Both buyers and sellers are required to leave feedback when they are finished with a transaction. This is used to calculate the score and color seen by each username.<br /><br />

                                There are two kinds of feedback, buyer feedback and seller feedback. Sellers get to see buyer feedback before accepting the transaction, and buyers get to see the seller's score and feedback on the listing page.
                            </div><!-- /.accordion-inner -->
                        </div><!-- /.accordion-body -->
                    </div><!-- /.accordion-group -->

                </div><!-- /.accordion -->
